java.lang.Object
org.postgresql.pljava.Adapter.Service
org.postgresql.pljava.pg.adt.Service
public final class Service extends Adapter.Service
Implementation of a service defined by Adapter for data types.

Handles operations such as creating a properly-typed ArrayAdapter with dimensions and types computed from an adapter for the component type.
